Art Block Meme by *golddemona on deviantART

Well, seeing as I don't own a laptop, I'd have to say that I don't bring mine on vacation.

......But if I DID have one, I have no doubt that I would, simply because I am addicted to the internet, and I can't survive a week without having checked my DeviantArt at least fifty thousand times. =P

It seems that every time I come back here, I wind up having to change up my journal cuz the layout and style I had when I left is always out of date. =P
For the most part when I want to post a journal entry, I just post on my DeviantArt journal. lol =P

I'm kinda sad that I almost never post anything to my LiveJournal.
Problem is I never know what to talk about in these things. =/
I also have a blog on BlogSpot, but I only have like two entries in it. D=
Just about everything I want to talk about pertains to my art, and so I pretty much cover all that in my DeviantArt journal.
I almost never have anything to talk about besides that. =/

Although going by the lack of comments on all my previous entries, it doesn't look like it really matters. lol XD

IF YOU'RE ON MY FRIENDS LIST (and have a moment to spare) I would like to know 36 things about you. I don't care if we never talk, or if we already know everything about each other. Short and sweet is fine...You're on my list, so I want to know you better!

BE HONEST. COPY FROM HERE, SEND DIRECTLY TO ME IN A COMMENT OR MY SPACE MESSAGE, THEN REPOST THE EMPTY QUESTIONS IF YOU WISH.

1) Are you currently in a serious relationship?

2) What was your dream growing up?

3) What talent do you wish you had?

4) If I bought you a drink what would it be?

5) Favorite vegetable?

6) What was the last book you read?

7) What zodiac sign are you?

8) Any Tattoos and/or Piercings? Explain where.

9) Worst Habit?

10) If you saw me walking down the street would you offer me a ride?

11) What is your favorite sport?

12) Do you have a Negative or Optimistic attitude?

13) What would you do if you were stuck in an elevator with me?

14) Worst thing to ever happen to you?

15) Tell me one weird fact about you.

16) Do you have any pets?

17) What if I showed up at your house unexpectedly?

18) What was your first impression of me?

19) Do you think clowns are cute or scary?

20) If you could change one thing about how you look, what would it be?

21) Would you be my crime partner or my conscience?

22) What color eyes do you have?

23) Ever been arrested?

24) Bottle or can soda?

25) If you won $10,000 today, what would you do with it?

27) What's your favorite place to hang at?

28) Do you believe in ghosts?

29) Favorite thing to do in your spare time?

30) Do you swear a lot?

31) Biggest pet peeve?

32) In one word, how would you describe yourself?

33) Do you believe/appreciate romance?

35) Do you believe in God?

36) Will you repost this so I can fill it out and do the same for you?

Was originally gonna be the first Friday of June 2006.
Now it will be the first SATURDAY of June 2006.
Now it's a little more convenient for all my guests. ^_^
Makes it more likely they'll be able to come. ^_^

This is my first entry in my brand spankin' new LiveJournal.
It's a lot easier to gt an LJ than a DJ. No stupid serial-number-ish codes to retrieve from friends and junk.
The bummer, though is that I was forced to use a password I'll probably never remember, because the password I normally use for everything has letters that repeat too close together, and LJ didn't like that.
Other than that, I'd say it's about the same as DJ, accept it's Live instead of Dead... I'm tired. I think I'll shut up now..
I guess this'll be it until I can do more with it.
